@maht0rz

> with a bit of extra work it could be passed in
to expand on that, you could wrap your merkle tree in an `Unconstrained` and pass it to the circuit:
```ts
@method myMethod(wrappedTree: Unconstrained<MerkleTree>) {

   let witness = Provable.witness(MyMerkleWitness, () => {
      let tree: MerkleTree = wrappedTree.get();
       // create merkle witness
   });
}
```

outside the circuit:
```ts
let wrappedTree = Unconstrained.from(tree);
myMethod(wrappedTree);
```
